import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 7))
    ax.boxplot(data['Penicillin'])
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of Penicillin across all bacteria?')
    ax.axhline(data['Penicillin'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Median: {data["Penicillin"].median():.2f}')
    ax.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()

    plt.title('What is the relationship between Streptomycin and Neomycin?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    gram_positive = data[data['Gram_Staining'] == 'positive']
    streptomycin = gram_positive['Streptomycin']
    plt.hist(streptomycin, bins=10, color='green')
    plt.axvline(streptomycin.mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {streptomycin.mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(streptomycin.median(), color='blue', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {streptomycin.median():.2f}")
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Streptomycin for Gram-positive bacteria?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    gram_negative = data[data['Gram_Staining'] == 'negative']
    neomycin = gram_negative['Neomycin']
    plt.hist(neomycin, bins=20, color='green')
    plt.axvline(neomycin.mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Mean = {neomycin.mean():.2f}')
    plt.axvline(neomycin.median(), color='blue', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Median = {neomycin.median():.2f}')
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Neomycin for Gram-negative bacteria?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    genus_count = data.groupby('Genus').size().reset_index(name='count')
    genus_count = genus_count.sort_values('count', ascending=False)
    plt.bar(genus_count['Genus'], genus_count['count'], color=['#1f77b4', '#ff7f0e', '#2ca02c', '#d62728'])
    plt.title('What is the most common genus of bacteria in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
